reviews.text: Traditional Chinese Medicine!

Seriously is this the place people  come to to get better or insulted for being human. I am shocked at the way staff here treat their patients...they have no feeling of compassion let alone sorry for almost injecting my son with the wrong drug. A nurse puts up a drip over the patient's head only to have droplets fall on him .....what if it went into his eye?? My son was choking on his vomit and guess what? even after pressing the nurse alert button an amah comes not able to offer any help.  Please do tell me who I should be speaking to about this treatment. I am not a local chinese but I have grown up here. How can they be so mean!!!
